    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "A meta-issue to track various proposed improvements to the project creation flow.\r\n\r\nThings we've actively discussed include:\r\n\r\n* [ ] Validation as you type  --- besides improving UX, this would sidestep rogue file generation on creation failures #1058\r\n* [ ] Project name proposals #1093\r\n* [x] Affordances to trigger an SDK installation flow #764\r\n* [ ] General reconsideration of the up-frontness of SDK config prompt #734\r\n* [ ] Improved `flutter create` progress reporting #734\r\n* [ ] General tidying up of unnecessary configuration options\r\n* [ ] Nice branding (a la Android Studio)\r\n\r\nAs a first cut, we'd like to experiment with something trimmed down like\r\n\r\n![image](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/67586/26856250-91158c76-4ad7-11e7-946e-4c3f4d6d5054.png)\r\n\r\nand add details as needed.\r\n\r\nDown the road we could consider adding\r\n\r\n* [ ] Template generation (a la stagehand) #1047\r\n* [x] Plugin project support",
